# Licensing

This software is available under a dual licensing model. It is licensed under the General Public License (GPL) for open source projects. For use in proprietary or commercial software, a commercial license is required.

## General Public License (GPL)

This software is licensed under the [GPL](https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html). You are free to use, modify, and distribute this software in open source projects as long as any derivative works are also licensed under the GPL.

## Commercial License

For use in proprietary or commercial projects, a commercial license must be obtained. This allows you to use, modify, and distribute the software without the requirements of the GPL.

To obtain a commercial license, please contact us at atendimento@ucode.com.br.

